#Artificialintelligence now plays a powerful role in how we see the world, see each other and see ourselves.⠀
⠀
#TrainingHumans considers training images of humans. The first floor explores the earliest training images used in scientific laboratories and the military. The second floor brings us into the age of the Internet and social media.⠀
⠀
on view at @fondazioneprada #Osservatorio until 24 Feb⠀
more via link in bio⠀
#fondazioneprada #trevorpaglen #katecrawford

The exhibition #TrainingHumans addresses an extremely topical issue: the evolution of machinic visual culture, the way artificial intelligence (AI) systems categorize the whole world.⠀
⠀
A project by #TrevorPaglen and #KateCrawford, on view at Osservatorio until 24 February 2020⠀
find out more via link in bio⠀
#fondazioneprada #osservatorio⠀
Ph. @_marcocappelletti

On the sixth floor of @fondazioneprada #Osservatorio CROSS-AGE CELEBRITY DATASET (2014) presents a collection of more than 160.000 images of 2.000 celebrities at various ages used by AI systems to classify people by age.⠀
⠀
The work is part of #TrainingHumans, the exhibition that explores how humans are represented, interpreted and codified through training datasets. ⠀
On view until 24 Feb 2020⠀
#fondazioneprada #trevorpaglen #katecrawford

“Zombi is a figure that people never speak about, whose existence some deny entirely” @bertrandbonello⠀
⠀
The special screening of #ZombiChild  took place yesterday but the film will be screened only and exclusively at @fondazioneprada #Cinema again in January and February 2020.⠀
⠀
#ZombiChild is also available in streaming on @mubi starting from today.⠀
⠀
#fondazioneprada #mubi ⠀
Ph. Ugo Dalla Porta

Since as a viewer, the French director @bertrandbonello came to cinema through the horror genre. ⠀
⠀
Last night he retraced his film career and introduced his latest work #ZombiChild in a conversation with actress @Louloulabek moderated by Luigi Alberto Cippini, at @fondazioneprada Cinema⠀
⠀
The event was realized in partnership with @mubi in the presence of his CEO Efe Cakarel⠀
#fondazioneprada #mubi ⠀
Ph. Ugo Dalla Porta

#ZombiChild special preview at @fondazioneprada #Cinema⠀
⠀
Yesterday night @bertrandbonello together with actress and protagonist Louise Labèque (@louloulabek) introduced the film to the public.⠀
⠀
#ZombiChild will be presented exclusively at Fondazione Prada Cinema in January and February 2020 thanks to @mubi ⠀
⠀
#fondazioneprada #mubi⠀

"Il sarcofago di Spitzmaus e altri tesori" closes in less than a month⠀
⠀
An exhibition imagined as a #wunderkammer by #WesAnderson and #JumanMalouf, a collection that pays homage to the coffin of a Spitzmaus, an Egyptian wooden box from the 4th century BC⠀
⠀
Design by @itai.margula 
on view until 13 Jan 2020⠀
#fondazioneprada #spitzmaus⠀
Ph. @andrea_rossetti_archive

This Friday you can visit the exhibition "Il sarcofago di Spitzmaus e altri tesori" with a member of @fondazioneprada's team⠀
⠀
Once a week curators, registrars and communication team introduce visitors to the project conceived by #WesAnderson and #JumanMalouf, sharing backstage stories and describing their own role in the creative process.⠀
⠀
Friday at 4.30PM - free upon booking⠀
discover more online ⠀
Ph. @andrea_rossetti_archive
Exhibition design by Wes Anderson and Juman Malouf with @itai.margula

In the interview with curators Jasper Sharp from @kunsthistorischesmuseumvienna and Mario Mainetti from @fondazioneprada -

The exhibition conceived by #WesAnderson and #JumanMalouf is on view until 13 Jan 2020

Despite the most popular American version "zombie", #zombi is the original term that represents a figure deeply rooted in the history and culture of Haiti.⠀
⠀
On 19 December Bertrand Bonello (@bertrandbonello) will present his latest film #ZombiChild at @fondazioneprada #Cinema. ⠀
⠀
The special screening starts at 8.30PM - free upon booking.⠀
⠀
Discover how to participate via link in bio⠀
#fondazioneprada #bertrandbonello #zombichild⠀
an event in collaboration with @mubi

#SaveTheDate: Thursday 19 Dec 8.30PM⠀
⠀
#ZombiChild special screening introduced by Bertrand Bonello (@bertrandbonello) and actress Louise Labèque (@louloulabek)⠀
⠀
Zombi Child is a bracingly original horror exploring the legacy of French colonialism in Haiti. Directed by Bertrand Bonello, the film has been presented in the Directors’ Fortnight section at @festivaldecannes, #TorontoInternationalFilmFestival, the @britishfilminstitute London Film Festival and @romacinemafest⠀
⠀
discover more via link in bio⠀
#fondazioneprada #cinema #bertrandbonello⠀
an event in collaboration with @mubi

Another special screening at @fondazioneprada Cinema⠀⠀
Thursday 19 Dec at 8:30PM ⠀
 Zombi Child the new film by Bertrand Bonello⠀⠀
⠀⠀
The special screening in partnership with @mubi will be introduced by a conversation between the director, the actress Louise Labèque @louloulabek and Luigi Alberto Cippini. The film will be screened in its original French version with English subtitles.⠀⠀
⠀⠀
the event is free upon booking⠀⠀
discover more on fondazioneprada.org⠀⠀
#zombichilad #fondazioneprada #bertrandbonello

There's a book left on the floor in the middle of Jean-Luc Godard's atelier, written by his wife Anne-Marie Miéville.

All the elements of “Le Studio d’Orphée” tell something about Jean-Luc Godard, creating an emotional geography within which visitors are invited to live an experience of exploration.

Ph. Agostino Osio / @altopianostudio 
#fondazioneprada #jeanlucgodard

"Le Studio d'Orphée" hosts Jean-Luc Godard's personal belongings, like books, objects and some of his awards.⠀
⠀
Within the atelier, visitors will have the unique opportunity to attend the screening of his latest film "Le Livre d’image" (2018) and a selection of nine short movies.⠀
⠀
Ph. Agostino Osio / @altopianostudio⠀
#fondazioneprada #jeanlucgodard

From Rolle to Milan, Jean-Luc Godard's atelier opens at @fondazioneprada⠀
⠀
"Le Studio d'Orphèe" is open from Wednesday to Monday from 1pm. The permanent installation offers the chance to enter in the director's living and work space, discovering all the details of his creative process.⠀
⠀
Ph. Agostino Osio /@altopianostudio⠀
discover more via link in bio⠀
#fondazioneprada #jeanlucgodard
